        <div class="card-title">Expect real alpha issues</div>
        <p class="card-body">
          SilkMC is not pretending to be production-perfect yet. There may still be security vulnerabilities,
          memory leaks, plugin edge cases, and rough failure modes while the compatibility layer matures.
        </p>
