          <div class="card-feat-left">
            <span class="card-icon">F</span>
            <div class="card-title">Fail closed when plugins go unsafe</div>
            <p class="card-body">
              If a plugin crosses known unsafe thread boundaries, SilkMC disables it cleanly and logs a direct
              compatibility warning instead of letting the whole server crash or spiral into loader fallout.
            </p>
            <span class="card-chip blue">protect the server first</span>
          </div>
